<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.5.10">
<l>karumamuṅ karuma palaṉu mākiya kāraṇaṉ ṟaṉṉait</l>
<l>tirumaṇi vaṇṇaṉaic ceṅkaṇ māliṉait tēva pirāṉai</l>
<l>yorumai maṉatti ṉuḷvait tuḷḷaṅ kuḻainteḻun tāṭip</l>
<l>perumaiyu nāṇun tavirntu pitaṟṟumiṉ pētaimai tīrntē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The cause who is karma and the fruit of karma,</l>
<l>the one of luminous sapphire colour, red-eyed Māl, the godly lord,</l>
<l>placing him in oneness in [your] minds, [your] hearts melting, rising, dancing</l>
<l>refraining from loftiness and shame babble, folly ending.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
